title: Chemical weapons experts enter Syrian attack town
text:
Chemical weapons experts enter Syrian attack town 8:50pm BST - 01:09 
Global chemical weapons experts finally reached the Syrian town of Douma on Tuesday, amid fears that evidence of an alleged chemical weapons attack there will now have been cleaned up. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
